oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Footlocker for William Carr Crenshaw
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This rectangular trunk is fitted with a lift out tray. The interior is lined with horizontally striped two tone brown paper. A metal label identifies the manufacturer as "ROGERS & MADISON TRUNK COMPANY." The exterior is finished in a dark green paint with reinforced edges and corners. Pvt. William C. Crenshaw served in Co. D, 117th Inf., 30th Div.
